episodes.title: Coffee Chat -- Ian's Cult Story
episodes.description: Grab a cup and join us as we talk about Ian's experience with a cult when he was a young kid. If you are not watching this one might I suggest that you do as our facial expressions and physical banter make the episode. Want to put a little apology in here for any offensive comments unintentionally made. Scott Patterson, it would literally be a dream to have a conversation with you….I think I may have to invest in some Luke’s mugs and coffee blends for our future chats on the channel! What kind of randomness would you like to hear from us in the future?!
